# BuildKit reads this file (Dockerfile.dockerignore next to the -f Dockerfile)
# when building `docker/Dockerfile` with the repository root as context. The
# Dockerfile is read directly via -f, so the context only needs the binary that
# the image COPYs in; everything else is excluded to keep the context small.
**
!target/
!target/release/
!target/release/nockchain
